<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I know PHP5.3 hasn't even entered RC stage, but I wanted to start using late static binding.</p>

<p>Certain keywords have been added to PHP5.3, for example goto.</p>

<p>Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_Redirector uses goto as a method name and so causes a parse error
"Parse error: syntax error, unexpected T_GOTO, expecting T_STRING"</p>

    </div>
